AI Practical #4 ‚Äî Marvel Character Article & Quiz | EN ‚áÑ RU
üìò Project Overview

EN:
This README documents the results for the ‚ÄúFourth practical task in AI.‚Äù The assignment requires using a generative AI tool (e.g., ChatGPT or Gemini) to:

Write an article about any Marvel character based strictly on that character‚Äôs Wikipedia page.

Explicitly define the article‚Äôs structure (headings, paragraph counts, etc.) and target audience.

Use the monologue format where the character speaks about themselves.

Perform a quality check after generation and, if quality is poor, create a revised version.

Create an English quiz based on the Wikipedia article with a limited number of questions, including: single-answer multiple choice, multiple-answer multiple choice, and true/false. Define the number of options and the correctness criteria, then quality-check and iterate if needed. 

AI fourth 4.0.0

