üß© Task 1 ‚Äî Article Generation (Monologue)

EN:
Goal: Create a first-person monologue article about a chosen Marvel character using only facts from the character‚Äôs Wikipedia page. Include a clearly declared structure and target audience. 

AI fourth 4.0.0

Actions performed:

Selected a Marvel character and located their official Wikipedia page.

Planned the article skeleton:

Title hierarchy (H1‚ÄìH3),

Number of sections and paragraphs per section,

Tone: first-person monologue,

Target audience definition.

Prompted a generative AI tool with: source constraint (Wikipedia only), structure, audience, and monologue requirement.

Performed a quality check: factual consistency with Wikipedia, clarity, cohesion, and style adherence.

If quality was subpar, iterated with refined prompts and corrections per issues found.

