üß© Task 2 ‚Äî English Quiz Creation

EN:
Goal: Build an English quiz about the same character based on the Wikipedia article, with a limited number of questions spanning three types:

Multiple choice (single correct),

Multiple choice (multiple correct),

True/False.
Define the number of options and how correctness is determined, then review and revise for quality. 

AI fourth 4.0.0

Actions performed:

Extracted key facts from the Wikipedia-based article.

Designed the quiz blueprint: question count cap; distribution across the three required types; per-question option counts; correctness rules.

Prompted AI to generate the quiz according to the blueprint.

Validated answers strictly against the Wikipedia source; corrected any drift.

If quality issues were found, regenerated or edited items and re-validated.

